      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "<p>The infrared spectrum of the compound with the following mass spectrum has a medium-intensity peak at about 1650 cm<sup>–1</sup>. There is also a C–H out-of-plane bending peak near 880 cm<sup>–1</sup>. Propose a structure.</p>\n<img src=\"https://exercises.openstax.org/rails/active_storage/blobs/proxy/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBaWNVIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--9d2bf287a1dfacb3e8e0456106d865164271c8ed/OChem_12_EC_015.jpg\" alt=\"The mass spectrum of  an uknown compound with a base peak at m / z 56 and a molecular ion at 84. Other significant peaks occur at 41 and 69.\">",
